<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 9800 - FULLER 10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS - DISASSEMBLE - MAINSHAFT
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="disassemble" graphiccount="2">
        <title>MAINSHAFT</title>
        <para>Refer to
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1303287">Figure 87</hotlnk>.
        </para>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Lay all parts on a clean bench in order of removal to facilitate assembly.</para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Lay the mainshaft on its side, and remove the front sliding clutch.</para>
        </step1>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>After removing the sliding clutch, clamp the front of the mainshaft in a vise with brass jaw
                    protectors to make disassembly easier.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Pull the mainshaft key from the mainshaft keyway from the rear of the mainshaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1303288">Figure 88</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Turn the reverse gear thrust washer to align its splines with the mainshaft and remove the
                washer and reverse gear (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1303288">Figure 88</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the sliding clutch (Figure 88).</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the washer and gear.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Turn the washer to align its splines with the mainshaft. Remove the washer and gear.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the remaining washers, gears, and sliding clutches.</para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1303287" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg13/G1303287.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" resolution="72"/>
            <caption>Figure 87. Mainshaft Disassembly</caption>
        </figure>
        <figure id="f1303288" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg13/G1303288.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="232px" resolution="72"/>
            <caption>Figure 88. Remove Sliding Clutch</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
